snippet.title: Sofia? [Release Trailer]
snippet.description:
Out now! Download for free today: https://hatoge.itch.io/sofia

Sofia? is a queer RPG Maker adventure mystery game where you spent a nice evening with your boyfriend... or do you?

A game by Hatoge
